# Plan: `@prisma/rest-api-client-generator`

## Context

Add a new Prisma generator package at `packages/rest-api-client-generator/` that implements the standard Prisma generator protocol. When a user adds it to their `prisma.config.ts` / `schema.prisma`, running `prisma generate` produces a typed TypeScript REST API client in the configured output directory. For every Prisma model the generator emits a TypeScript interface, `CreateInput`/`UpdateInput` type aliases, and a class with the five CRUD methods (`findMany`, `findUnique`, `create`, `update`, `delete`). A top-level `RestApiClient` class composes all per-model clients as properties.

---

## Files to create

```
packages/rest-api-client-generator/
├── .gitignore
├── helpers/build.ts
├── package.json
├── tsconfig.json
├── tsconfig.build.json
└── src/
    ├── index.ts               ← generator entry point (generatorHandler)
    ├── generate-client.ts     ← orchestrator: resolves output dir, writes files
    ├── field-type-mapper.ts   ← DMMF field → TypeScript type string
    ├── types-file.ts          ← generates types.ts content
    ├── client-file.ts         ← generates rest-api-client.ts content
    └── __tests__/
        ├── field-type-mapper.test.ts
        ├── types-file.test.ts
        └── client-file.test.ts
```

## Files to modify

- `tsconfig.build.bundle.json` — add one path entry
- `.github/workflows/test-template.yml` — add one test step in the `others` job (after line 862, after the `generator` step)

---

## Output files (generated into user's output dir)

| File | Content |
|---|---|
| `types.ts` | Enum union types, model interfaces, `CreateInput`/`UpdateInput` type aliases |
| `rest-api-client.ts` | Per-model client classes + `RestApiClient` composer |
| `index.ts` | `export * from './types'; export * from './rest-api-client'` |

---

## Step-by-step implementation

### 1. Package boilerplate

**`package.json`** — mirrors `@prisma/debug` plus `bin` (required for Prisma to spawn it as a process) and workspace dependencies:

```json
{
  "name": "@prisma/rest-api-client-generator",
  "version": "0.0.0",
  "description": "Prisma generator that produces a typed TypeScript REST API client",
  "main": "dist/index.js",
  "module": "dist/index.mjs",
  "types": "dist/index.d.ts",
  "exports": {
    ".": {
      "require": { "types": "./dist/index.d.ts", "default": "./dist/index.js" },
      "import": { "types": "./dist/index.d.mts", "default": "./dist/index.mjs" }
    }
  },
  "bin": {
    "prisma-rest-api-client-generator": "dist/index.js"
  },
  "license": "Apache-2.0",
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://github.com/prisma/prisma.git",
    "directory": "packages/rest-api-client-generator"
  },
  "homepage": "https://www.prisma.io",
  "bugs": "https://github.com/prisma/prisma/issues",
  "dependencies": {
    "@prisma/dmmf": "workspace:*",
    "@prisma/generator": "workspace:*",
    "@prisma/generator-helper": "workspace:*"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@types/node": "~20.19.24",
    "typescript": "5.4.5"
  },
